  "remarks": "JSC Beto is a Russian military-industrial enterprise that develops telecommunications systems, including radio receivers, which are deployed by the Russian Armed Forces. JSC Beto holds several contracts with the Russian Ministry of Defence and with the Department of Material and Technical Supply of the Ministry of Internal Affairs of the Russian Federation. JSC Beto is therefore supporting materially and benefitting from the Government of the Russian Federation, which is responsible for the annexation of Crimea and the destabilisation of Ukraine.",
